1
00:00:11,420 --> 00:00:12,460
My husband.

2
00:00:19,790 --> 00:00:20,790
Does he still want me?

3
00:00:23,630 --> 00:00:24,630
Is having an affair.

4
00:00:26,540 --> 00:00:28,210
My husband's mistress is...

5
00:00:37,660 --> 00:00:38,660
Cheers!

6
00:00:47,790 --> 00:00:49,750
The president of Kurogane Holdings,

7
00:00:49,750 --> 00:00:51,040
Mr. Kurogane Samon,

8
00:00:51,540 --> 00:00:52,540
for President Nakama,

9
00:00:52,750 --> 00:00:53,290
has specially recorded

10
00:00:53,290 --> 00:00:54,630
a congratulatory video message.

11
00:00:55,130 --> 00:00:56,460
From President Kurogane?

12
00:00:56,750 --> 00:00:58,170
Wow, President Kurogane himself.
Incredible.

13
00:00:58,750 --> 00:01:00,290
That's the famous handsome president for you.

14
00:01:00,750 --> 00:01:02,830
Kurogane's market cap is over a trillion, isn't it?

15
00:01:02,830 --> 00:01:04,290
Oh, that's right.

16
00:01:04,500 --> 00:01:06,250
You're really something, President!

17
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:07,750
You're too kind.

18
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:10,710
This is all thanks to
everyone's dedicated support

19
00:01:10,710 --> 00:01:11,710
that we've achieved what we have today.

20
00:01:12,040 --> 00:01:12,670
Alright then.

21
00:01:12,790 --> 00:01:14,670
It looks like the roast beef
has arrived.

22
00:01:14,880 --> 00:01:17,080
My wife's cooking
is out of this world.

23
00:01:17,710 --> 00:01:19,130
Please, everyone, dig in.

24
00:01:19,330 --> 00:01:20,250
Aaaah!

25
00:01:20,290 --> 00:01:22,960
There's... there's a bug!

26
00:01:23,250 --> 00:01:25,290
There's a bug... in the food!

27
00:01:25,290 --> 00:01:26,540
This is unbelievable.

28
00:01:26,630 --> 00:01:28,130
A bug this huge!

29
00:01:28,130 --> 00:01:29,710
A bug this huge!

30
00:01:30,630 --> 00:01:33,000
What is going on
at this party?!

31
00:01:33,080 --> 00:01:34,460
President, this is a disaster!

32
00:01:34,580 --> 00:01:35,830
We were on the verge of signing
with Koda-san's company

33
00:01:35,830 --> 00:01:37,250
for the cloud service

34
00:01:37,380 --> 00:01:38,380
joint development

35
00:01:38,460 --> 00:01:39,920
business partnership.

36
00:01:39,920 --> 00:01:41,170
This project was all set to go.

37
00:01:41,170 --> 00:01:42,170
At this rate...

38
00:01:42,170 --> 00:01:43,670
President Nakama's wife.

39
00:01:43,670 --> 00:01:45,920
You were in charge of the food, correct?

40
00:01:46,380 --> 00:01:47,540
Explain yourself!

41
00:01:47,830 --> 00:01:48,960
Explain yourself!

42
00:01:48,960 --> 00:01:50,170
I am terribly sorry.

43
00:01:50,420 --> 00:01:51,830
But... something like this...
should be impossible.

44
00:01:51,880 --> 00:01:52,540
Shut your mouth!

45
00:01:52,790 --> 00:01:54,210
The fact is, there's a bug in the food.

46
00:01:54,210 --> 00:01:57,250
For someone from a poor,
single-parent home...

47
00:01:57,250 --> 00:01:59,170
you have some nerve talking back to me.

48
00:01:59,170 --> 00:02:00,040
My upbringing has nothing to do with this.

49
00:02:00,040 --> 00:02:01,040
I said, shut up!

50
00:02:01,250 --> 00:02:04,420
A person who's only good for making bug bait.

51
00:02:04,420 --> 00:02:05,420
If you want to make excuses,

52
00:02:05,580 --> 00:02:07,080
at least learn how to make
food fit for human consumption

53
00:02:07,080 --> 00:02:08,330
first!

54
00:02:19,380 --> 00:02:20,380
Apologize.

55
00:02:22,580 --> 00:02:24,130
For the company's sake, apologize.

56
00:02:24,580 --> 00:02:26,670
Be an adult about this, understand?

57
00:02:30,580 --> 00:02:31,420
I'm sor—

58
00:02:31,420 --> 00:02:32,750
The words are, "I am deeply sorry."

59
00:02:33,290 --> 00:02:34,080
I am deeply sorry.

60
00:02:34,080 --> 00:02:35,130
Your head!

61
00:02:35,580 --> 00:02:37,380
You bow your head when you apologize.

62
00:02:37,960 --> 00:02:38,790
I am deeply sorry.

63
00:02:38,790 --> 00:02:40,130
Lower!

64
00:02:40,130 --> 00:02:41,580
That's not nearly low enough.

65
00:02:41,580 --> 00:02:43,670
Your head is still miles
from the floor, isn't it?

66
00:02:43,960 --> 00:02:45,880
I want that head of yours
buried in the floor.

67
00:02:55,880 --> 00:02:57,290
Excuse me, I believe you dropped this.

68
00:02:57,630 --> 00:02:59,000
That woman...

69
00:02:59,420 --> 00:03:00,080
She is...

70
00:03:00,420 --> 00:03:01,920
my husband's mistress.

71
00:03:02,380 --> 00:03:03,380
And...

72
00:03:05,130 --> 00:03:06,960
she's my ex-girlfriend.
